---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Best Webcam for Work from Home 2026';
const pageDescription = 'Honest review of 1080p webcams. Look professional on Zoom calls without spending $200.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} />
    <style>
      main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #232f3e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .product-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .product-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
      .product-box ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #ff9900; color: #000; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
      .disclaimer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best Webcam for Work from Home</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated May 2026 · 1080p Full HD</div>

      <p>If you work from home, a good webcam is essential for looking professional on video calls. After testing multiple 1080p webcams, one stands out for its reliable quality and affordable price point — no need to spend $200 on a premium model.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>🏆 Logitech C920 HD Pro</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Full HD 1080p video at 30fps</strong> — crystal clear video quality</li>
          <li><strong>Stereo audio with dual microphones</strong> — natural sound pickup</li>
          <li><strong>Automatic light correction</strong> — adjusts to any lighting condition</li>
          <li><strong>Plug-and-play USB connection</strong> — no drivers needed</li>
          <li><strong>Universal clip fits laptops and monitors</strong> — versatile mounting</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=logitech+c920&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why it wins at this price</h3>
      <p>Most budget webcams compromise on video quality or low-light performance. The Logitech C920 delivers consistent 1080p video with excellent auto-exposure, making you look sharp even in dimly lit rooms. The built-in stereo microphones are surprisingly clear for built-in audio.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Remote workers, streamers, and anyone who wants professional-looking video calls without breaking the bank. It's perfect for Zoom meetings, Google Meet, and even basic content creation.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>